ğŸ§ª API Endpoints Overview
POST
/users/
Register a new user
GET
/users/{user_id}
Get user details by ID
POST
/tasks/
Add a new task
GET
/tasks/{task_id}
Get task details by ID
PUT
/tasks/{task_id}
Update task status
GET
/users/{user_id}/tasks
Get all tasks assigned to a user

